To build a static library such that it can be used by Apple, for now do

    cabal build cob-swift $(echo $STATIC_HASKELL_CABAL_OPTS)

(The echo is needed to expand the var)
This makes sure the resulting library is statically linked against everything except libSystem
Check out my static_haskell module and

    otool -L path-to-flib.dylib

to see only libSystem is dynlinked
